      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>GlobalExceptionHandler 与 Flyway Migration 策略</strong></p>
  - elementId: p14-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 78, 1160, 2]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: p14-left-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 95, 300, 30]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 18
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>统一异常处理体系</strong></p>
  - elementId: p14-left-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 135, 560, 510]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: p14-left-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 150, 520, 480]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 14
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:$primary;">ApiResponse&lt;T&gt; 统一包装</strong></p>
        <p>· code / data / message / timestamp / traceId</p>
        <p>· FieldError: field / message / rejectedValue</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">ErrorCode 枚举（6位编码）</strong></p>
        <p>· 000000 SUCCESS | 000001 INTERNAL_ERROR</p>
        <p>· 000002 BAD_REQUEST | 000003 NOT_FOUND</p>
        <p>· 002001 VALIDATION_ERROR</p>
        <p>· 001001 USER_NOT_FOUND | 001002 USER_ALREADY_EXISTS</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">三层异常处理</strong></p>
        <p>1. BusinessException → 业务异常，返回对应 ErrorCode</p>
        <p>2. MethodArgumentNotValidException → 参数校验，返回 VALIDATION_ERROR + errors 数组</p>
        <p>3. Exception → 兜底异常，返回 INTERNAL_ERROR</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">X-Trace-Id 全链路追踪</strong></p>
        <p>· 优先读取请求头已有 TraceId</p>
        <p>· 否则生成 16位 UUID 子串</p>
  - elementId: p14-right-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 95, 300, 30]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 18
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Flyway Migration 策略</strong></p>
  - elementId: p14-right-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 135, 560, 530]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: p14-right-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 150, 520, 500]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 14
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:$primary;">目录结构</strong></p>
        <p>· db/migration/ — 核心 DDL（环境无关）</p>
        <p>· db/migration/mysql/ — MySQL 特有（可选）</p>
        <p>· db/test-migration/ — H2 测试数据</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">H2 兼容性规则</strong></p>
        <p>· AUTO_INCREMENT → GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY</p>
        <p>· ENGINE=InnoDB → 移除</p>
        <p>· CHARSET=utf8mb4 → 移除（H2 默认 UTF-8）</p>
        <p>· TIMESTAMP → TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE</p>
        <p>· INT → INTEGER 或 BIGINT</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">配置分层</strong></p>
        <p>· 生产：flyway.enabled=true，validate-on-migrate=true</p>
        <p>· 测试：H2 MODE=MySQL，clean-disabled=false</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$accent;">破坏性变更流程</strong></p>
        <p>1. 新增 Migration 文件（如 V4__add_user_phone.sql）</p>
        <p>2. 旧列保留，新增列，应用层双写</p>
        <p>3. 下一个版本 Migration 再清理旧列</p>
        <p>4. 更新 docs/design/adr/ 记录决策</p>
  - elementId: p14-page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1160, 690, 60, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "14"